0the%20strings%2C%20and%20the%20long%20sustain%20of%20each%20note.%20Vocals%20come%20alive%2C%20exposing%20every%20breath%20and%20even%20every%20micro%20movement%20between%20the%20singer%20and%20the%20microphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20aural%20feast%20for%20the%20senses%20that%20brings%20you%20closer%20to%20your%20favorite%20music%20than%20anything%20we've%20heard%20at%20this%20price%20point%20and%20even%20well%20above.%20The%20HD%206XX's%20one%20sonic%20drawback%2C%20if%20you%20can%20call%20it%20that%2C%20is%20that%20the%20bass%20is%20more%20resigned%20for%20a%20flatter%2C%20less%20accentuated%20punch.%20Those%20used%20to%20the%20heavier%20bass%20signatures%20of%20most%20wireless%20headphones%20may%20find%20it%20lacking%2C%20but%20it's%20enough%20to%20hold%20down%20the%20foundation%20and%20let%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20music%20flourish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20wires%2C%20these%20are%20plug-in%20only%2C%20connecting%20with%20a%20six-foot%20cable.%20They'll%20work%20with%20everything%20from%20a%20PC%20to%20a%20phone%20(with%20an%20adapter)%2C%20but%20they%20sound%20best%20if%20you%20drive%20them%20with%20a%20dedicated%20headphone%20amp.%20Perhaps%20most%20important%20to%20note%20is%20that%2C%20while%20their%20plush%20earcups%20make%20them%20comfortable%20for%20hours%2C%20their%20open-back%20design%20means%20that%20nothing%20you%20listen%20to%20is%20for%20you%20alone.%20Your%20music%20will%20spill%20out%20into%20the%20world%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HD%206XX%20don't%20come%20with%20a%20hard%20case%2C%20but%20then%20again%2C%20their%20exposed%20exterior%20means%20you'll%20likely%20want%20to%20listen%20mostly%20at%20home%20anyway.%20You%20won't%20get%20nearly%20the%20same%20versatility%20here%20as%20what's%20offered%20by%20our%20top%20pick%20or%20most%20wireless%20headphones.%20But%20if%20sound%20quality%20and%20comfort%20are%20your%20primary%20objectives%2C%20you%20simply%20won't%20find%20a%20better%20pair%20at%20this%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20premium%20model%5C%22%3EBest%20premium%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20makes%20you%20feel%20like%20part%20of%20the%20glitterati%20like%20a%20pair%20of%20headphones%20that%20actually%20glitter.%20Master%20%26amp%3B%20Dynamic's%20expensive%20MW75%20offer%20audio%20performance%20befitting%20of%20their%20price%20point%20and%20some%20solid%20features%20as%20well.%20But%20what%20really%20makes%20them%20special%20is%20their%20premium%20design%20that's%20equal%20parts%20stunning%20style%20and%20luxurious%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20earcups%20etched%20from%20sparkling%20aluminum%20and%20tempered%20glass%2C%20the%20headphones%20feel%20cool%20and%20sleek%20to%20the%20touch.%20Their%20simplified%20control%20system%20uses%20tactile%20aluminum%20keys%20along%20the%20right%20and%20left%20earcups%20for%20volume%20and%20playback%20commands.%20The%20cushy%20headband%20and%20earpads%20are%20cloaked%20in%20gorgeous%20lambskin%2C%20which%20looks%20especially%20lovely%20in%20cognac%20brown.%20They%20feel%20as%20soft%20as%20a%20law%20firm's%20couch%2C%20and%20though%20they%20get%20a%20little%20warm%20after%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20it's%20frankly%20hard%20to%20find%20much%20fault%20with%20anything%20that%20looks%20this%20cool.%20The%20earcups%20are%20also%20removable%20and%20replaceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20Master%20%26amp%3B%20Dynamic%20MW75%20headphones%20on%20a%20table%20next%20to%20a%20record%20player.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6604436c16bde8d4ead2a0a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaster%20%26amp%3B%20Dynamic's%20MW75%20feature%20a%20luxurious%20design.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20substance%20beneath%20that%20glam%20exterior%2C%20too.%20The%20headphones%20sound%20excellent%2C%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20pristine%20cl