20multipoint%20pairing%20to%20easily%20swap%20between%20multiple%20playback%20devices.%20The%20best%20over-ear%20headphones%20with%20wireless%20support%20should%20include%20an%20app%20to%20control%20settings%2C%20most%20notably%20an%20EQ%20(or%20equalizer)%20to%20adjust%20the%20sound.%20You'll%20also%20want%20to%20check%20the%20Bluetooth%20version%20used.%20We%20recommend%205.0%20or%20higher%20to%20ensure%20a%20seamless%20wireless%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20features%20aren't%20applicable%20if%20you're%20shopping%20for%20a%20wired%20pair%20of%20over-ear%20headphones%2C%20but%20whether%20you%20go%20wireless%20or%20wired%2C%20comfort%20is%20king.%20You'll%20want%20to%20ensure%20your%20pair%20isn't%20overly%20heavy%20and%20offers%20ample%20padding%20along%20the%20earcups%20and%20headband.%20Other%20important%20factors%20include%20the%20ability%20to%20fold%20for%20travel%20and%20accessories%20like%20a%20hard%20case%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20take%20your%20headphones%20on%20the%20go.%20For%20audiophile%20options%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20decide%20between%20open-back%20models%2C%20which%20generally%20offer%20a%20more%20airy%20soundstage%20but%20let%20in%20environmental%20noise%2C%20or%20closed-back%20models%2C%20which%20sound%20more%20static%20but%20are%20more%20versatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20your%20guiding%20force%20should%20be%20sound%20quality.%20Your%20headphones%20can%20have%20all%20the%20features%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20if%20they%20don't%20sound%20good%2C%20you%20won't%20want%20to%20use%20them.%20For%20help%20there%2C%20you%20can%20look%20at%20critical%20reviews%2C%20user%20reviews%2C%20and%20guides%20like%20this.%20You%20can%20generally%20trust%20top%20brands%20like%20Sony%2C%20Sennheiser%2C%20Bose%2C%20and%20Apple%20or%2C%20on%20the%20budget%20side%2C%20Soundcore.%20Sound%20is%20subjective%2C%20so%20whenever%20possible%2C%20we%20recommend%20trying%20a%20pair%20of%20headphones%20for%20yourself%20before%20you%20buy.%3C