%2C%20said%20she%20was%20hurt%20by%20the%20opposition%20leader's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(incident)%20sets%20the%20cause%20of%20women%20back%20by%20many%20years.%20She%20has%20posted%20a%20very%20alarming%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrinate%20had%20also%20hurt%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20by%20comparing%20Mandi%2C%20a%20'devbhoomi'%2C%20to%20a%20market%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meaning%20of%20Mandi%20is%20not%20what%20runs%20in%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Congress.%20The%20innocent%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20were%20deeply%20hurt%20when%20they%20branded%20it%20as%20if%20it%20was%20a%20flesh%20trade%20market.%20Mandi%20was%20named%20after%20sage%20Mandav%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20she%20had%20a%20message%20for%20Shrinate%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20said%20she%20has%20nothing%20to%20say%20to%20the%20Congress%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ranaut%20also%20said%20it's%20ironic%20how%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20joined%20politics%20with%20the%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20campaign%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20jail%20on%20corruption%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20her%20political%20debut%2C%20she%20said%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Banxious%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20complete%20lifestyle%20change.%20It's%20nerve-wracking.%20It's%20a%20new%20role...%20I%20will%20be%20a%20horse%20with%20blinkers%20on.%20Suddenly%20this%20world%20has%20opened%20up.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20it%20well.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20more%20involved%20with%20the%20real%20world%20as%20opposed%20to%20being%20consumed%20by%20the%20field%20of%20arts%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ranaut%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published