%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20normalcy%20that%20returns%20to%20where%20we%20are%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20troop%20deployment%20will%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20relationship%20going%20forward.%20And%20we've%20been%20very%2C%20very%20honest%20with%20the%20Chinese%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20China%2C%20the%20relationship%20has%20been%20difficult%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20a%20boundary%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20despite%20the%20boundary%20dispute%20over%20the%20many%20years%2C%20we%20built%20up%20a%20substantial%20relationship%20because%20we%20agreed%20that%20while%20we%20will%20negotiate%20the%20boundary%20dispute%2C%20both%20of%20us%20will%20agree%20that%20we%20will%20not%20bring%20soldiers%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20the%20boundary.%20And%20we%20will%20never%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20there'll%20be%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20understanding%20which%20started%20in%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20actually%20was%20reflected%20in%20several%20agreements.%20And%20those%20agreements%20gave%20the%20relationship%20stability%20based%20on%20which%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20the%20relationship%20went%20forward%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20for%20reasons%20still%20not%20clear%20to%20us%2C%20these%20agreements%20were%20broken%20in%202020.%20And%20we%20had%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20China%20nose-dived%20significantly%20following%20the%20deadly%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711555920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fpbi2ebo8_s-jaishankar_625x300_24_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnormalcy-in-ties-with-china-will-only-be-achieved-based-on-based-on-the-traditional-troop-deployment-s-jaishankar-5322177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20ties%20with%20China%20will%20only%20be%20achieved%20based%20on%20the%20traditional%20deployment%20of%20troops%20and%20will%20be%20the%20prerequisite%20for%20the%20relationship%20with%20Beijing%20in%20the%20future%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnormalcy-in-ties-with-china-will-only-be-achieved-based-on-based-on-the-traditional-troop-deployment-s-jaishankar-5322177%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Audio%20captures%20dispatchers'%20response%20to%20bridge%20collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711555823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE36F%2Fproduction%2F_133032285_p0hm9b1s.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68678214%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recording%20of%20emergency%20communications%20reveals%20the%20tense%20moments%20before%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapsed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-68678214%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Keep%20Our%20Courts%20Strong%26quot%3B%3A%20Bar%20Association%20In%20Letter%20To%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20Manipur%20Bar%20Association%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20highlighting%20the%20need%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20%26quot%3Bunderhanded%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20association%20in%20the%20letter%20said%20it%20is%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20recent%20trends%20where%20vested%20interest%20groups%20are%20trying%20to%20defame%20the%20courts%20with%20%26quot%3Bfrivolous%20logic%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bstale%20political%20agendas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20heated%20interest%20group%20operates%20in%20various%20ways.%20They%20create%20false%20narratives%20of%20a%20supposed%20'better%20past'%20and%20'golden%20period'%20of%20the%20courts%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bar%20association%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20nothing%20but%20intentional%20statements%20made%20to%20embarrass%20the%20courts%20for%20certain%20gains...%20Their%20pressure%20tactics%20are%20most%20obvious%20in%20political%20cases%2C%20particularly%20those%20involving%20political%20figures%20accused%20of%20corruption.%20These%20tactics%20are%20damaging%20to%20our%20courts%20and%20threaten%20our%20democratic%20fabric%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bar%20association%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20dated%20March%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20association%20requested%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20to%20take%20strong%20steps%20to%20protect%20the%20courts%20from%20such%20%26quot%3Battacks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20They%20have%20also%20stooped%20to%20the%20level%20of%20comparing%20our%20courts%20to%20those%20countries%20where%20there%20is%20no%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20accusing%20our%20judicial%20institutions%20with%20unfair%20practices.%20These%20aren't%20just%20criticisms%3B%20they%20are%20direct%20attacks%20meant%20to%20damage%20the%20public's%20trust%20in%20our%20judiciary%20and%20threaten%20the%20fair%20application%20of%20our%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bar%20association%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20people%20who%20work%20to%20uphold%20the%20law%2C%20we%20think%20it%20is%20time%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20our%20courts.%20We%20need%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20these%20underhanded%20attacks%2C%20making%20sure%20our%20courts%20stay%20strong%20as%20pillars%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20untouched%20by%20these%20calculated%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bar%20association%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%20All%20Manipur%20Bar%20Association%20president%20Puyam%20Tomcha%20Meetei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-ndtv-interview-no-case-too-small-for-highest-court-chief-justices-message-to-citizens-5277167%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20March%2020%20had%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20always%20there%20for%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Birrespective%20of%20wealth%2C%20social%20status%2C%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20or%20gender%20or%20who%20is%20in%20power%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20case%20is%20too%20small%20for%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20get%20emails%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20Once%20there%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20needed%20medical%20termination%20of%20a%20pregnancy...%20my%20staff%20contacted%20me%20and%20we%20constituted%20a%20Bench%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20said%2C%20giving%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711555440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Ftthv9vd8_supreme-court-india-generic-pti_625x300_10_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-keep-our-courts-strong-says-all-manipur-bar-association-in-letter-to-ch