-our-hearts-are-so-full-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F108826530.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22School%20head%20resigns%20over%20Paris%20veil%20death%20threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711554641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F55DE%2Fproduction%2F_133028912_gettyimages-486130906.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68673112%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20indignation%20in%20France%20after%20the%20principal%20at%20a%20Paris%20school%20quit%20because%20of%20fears%20for%20his%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68673112%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68673112.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68673112.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kate%20Middleton%20Not%20Alone.%20Cancer%20On%20Rise%20For%20People%20Under%2050%2C%20Say%20Experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Catherine%2C%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20revealed%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20cancer%20last%20week%2C%20part%20of%20the%20shock%20was%20that%20an%20otherwise%20healthy%2042-year-old%20has%20a%20disease%20that%20mostly%20plagues%20older%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20researchers%20have%20been%20increasingly%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20that%20more%20and%20more%20people%20under%2050%20are%20getting%20cancer%20--%20and%20no%20one%20knows%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20under-50s%20diagnosed%20with%2029%20common%20cancers%20surged%20by%20nearly%2080%20percent%20between%201990%20and%202019%2C%20a%20large%20study%20in%20BMJ%20Oncology%20found%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20predicted%20the%20number%20of%20new%20cancer%20cases%20among%20younger%20adults%20will%20rise%20another%2030%20percent%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade%2C%20with%20wealthy%20countries%20particularly%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20cases%20--%20and%20soaring%20global%20population%20--%20means%20that%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20among%20under%2050s%20from%20cancer%20has%20risen%20by%20nearly%2028%20percent%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20occurred%20even%20as%20the%20odds%20of%20people%20of%20all%20ages%20surviving%20cancer%20have%20roughly%20doubled%20over%20the%20last%20half%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivan%20Sivakumar%2C%20a%20cancer%20researcher%20at%20the%20UK's%20University%20of%20Birmingham%2C%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bepidemic%26quot%3B%20of%20young%20adult%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Kate%20Middleton%20revealed%20on%20Friday%20that%20her%20cancer%20was%20discovered%20after%20she%20received%20abdominal%20surgery%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Sivakumar%20and%20other%20doctors%20have%20spoken%20out%20about%20the%20uptick%20in%20younger%20cancer%20patients%20they%20have%20been%20seeing%20at%20their%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20breast%20cancer%20remains%20the%20most%20common%20for%20people%20under%2050%2C%20the%20researchers%20expressed%20particular%20concern%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20gastrointestinal%20cancers%20--%20such%20as%20of%20the%20colon%2C%20pancreas%2C%20liver%20and%20oesophagus%20--%20in%20younger%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColon%20cancer%20is%20now%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20cancer%20deaths%20in%20men%20under%2050%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Cancer%20Society.%20For%20women%2C%20it%20is%20number%20two%20--%20behind%20only%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20high%20profile%20case%20of%20colorectal%20cancer%20was%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Panther%26quot%3B%20actor%20Chadwick%20Boseman%2C%20who%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2043%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20happening%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20have%20the%20evidence%20yet%26quot%3B%20to%20say%20exactly%20what%20is%20causing%20this%20rise%2C%20Sivakumar%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20likely%20a%20combination%20of%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelen%20Coleman%2C%20a%20cancer%20epidemiology%20professor%20at%20Queen's%20University%20Belfast%20who%20has%20studied%20early%20onset%20cancer%20in%20Northern%20Ireland%2C%20told%20AFP%20there%20were%20two%20potential%20explanations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20that%20people%20in%20their%2040s%20were%20exposed%20to%20factors%20known%20to%20cause%20cancer%20--%20such%20tobacco%20smoke%2C%20alcohol%20or%20being%20obese%20--%20at%20an%20earlier%20age%20than%20previous%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bobesity%20epidemic%26quot%3B%20did%20not%20start%20until%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESivakumar%20felt%20that%20at%20least%20part%20of%20the%20puzzle%20could%20be%20explained%20by%20obesity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Banother%20wave%26quot%3B%20of%20under-50%20patients%20who%20are%20neither%20obese%20nor%20genetically%20predisposed%20still%20getting%20cancer%2C%20he%20emphasised%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20could%20not%20be%20put%20down%20to%20%26quot%3Bstatistical%20chance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20theory%2C%20Coleman%20said%2C%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20different%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20going%20on%20with%20her%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFingers%20have%20been%20pointed%20out%20a%20range%20of%20possible%20culprits%20--%20including%20chemicals%2C%20new%20drugs%20and%20microplastics%20--%20but%20none%20have%20been%20proven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20suggested%20that%20so-called%20ultra-processed%20foods%20could%20be%20to%20blame.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there's%20very%20little%20data%20to%20back%20any%20of%20that%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Coleman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20could%20be%20changing%20our%20gut%20microbiome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20nothing%20conclusive%20yet%2C%20Coleman%20said%20her%20own%20research%20suggested%20that%20cancer%20causes%20changes%20to%20the%20microbiome%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-vaxx%20conspiracy%20theorists%20have%20even%20tried%20to%20blame%20Covid-19%20vaccines.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20easily%20disproven%2C%20because%20the%20rise%20in%20young%20adult%20cancer%20has%20taken%20place%20over%20decades%2C%20but%20the%20vaccines%20have%20only%20been%20around%20for%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20be%20done%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20rise%20in%20younger%20colorectal%20cancer%2C%20in%202021%20the%20US%20lowered%20the%20recommended%20age%20for%20screening%20to%2045.%20Other%20countries%20have%20yet%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20researchers%20hoped%20that%20Catherine's%20experience%20would%20remind%20people%20at%20home%20that%20they%20should%20consult%20their%20doctor%20if%20they%20sense%20anything%20is%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20know%20their%20bodies%20really%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Sivakumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20really%20feel%20that%20something%20isn't%20right%2C%20don't%20delay%20--%20just%20get%20yourself%20checked%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711553160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv8se7gl_kate-middleton_625x300_25_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkate-middleton-not-alone-cancer-on-rise-for-people-under-50s-say-experts-5322117%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%