%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20long%20been%20isolated%20from%20the%20global%20community%2C%20enforcing%20strict%20controls%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20movement%2C%20and%20access%20to%20information.%20The%20country's%20poor%20human%20rights%20record%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Internet%20usage%20is%20severely%20restricted%2C%20and%20even%20those%20with%20access%20to%20smartphones%20are%20limited%20to%20a%20government-controlled%20and%20heavily%20censored%20intranet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20materials%20such%20as%20books%20and%20films%20are%20prohibited%2C%20with%20severe%20penalties%20for%20individuals%20caught%20possessing%20contraband%20obtained%20through%20the%20black%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711549860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fn4n795go_alan-titchmarsh-trousers_625x300_27_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnorth-korea-tv-censors-british-gardening-show-presenters-trousers-5321882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Titchmarsh%20joked%20that%20North%20Korea's%20censorship%20gave%20his%20gardening%20show%20some%20unexpected%20'street%20cred.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnorth-korea-tv-censors-british-gardening-show-presenters-trousers-5321882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20man%20dies%20in%20skiing%20accident%20'after%20hitting%20tree'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711549740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-avoriaz-ski-resort_6502482.jpg%3F20240327150236%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-man-dies-in-skiing-accident-in-france-after-hitting-tree-13102861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20man%20has%20died%20in%20a%20skiing%20accident%20in%20France.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%