20Gill's%20life%20savings%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20a%20substantial%20debt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian-origin%20doctor%20is%20a%20vocal%20critic%20against%20vaccination.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20not%20yet%20figured%20out%20that%20we%20don't%20need%20a%20vaccine%2C%20you%20are%20not%20paying%20attention.%20%23FactsNotFear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X%20in%20August%2C%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20posts%20were%20heavily%20criticised%20by%20the%20medical%20community%20and%20also%20by%20many%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media.%20Dr%20Gill%20sued%2023%20doctors%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20news%20outlets%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20were%20part%20of%20a%20defamation%20campaign%20against%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20was%20thrown%20out%20by%20a%20judge%20citing%20anti-SLAPP%20(Strategic%20Lawsuit%20Against%20Public%20Participation)%20law%2C%20stating%20that%20Dr%20Gill's%20intention%20was%20to%20stifle%20her%20critics'%20speech%20on%20a%20public%20platform.%20Dr%20Gill%20was%20instructed%20to%20cover%20the%20defendants'%20legal%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711547160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flhaoning_elon-musk-indian-origin-_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Felon-musk-to-pay-indian-origin-doctor-kulvinder-kaur-gill-rs-2-crore-legal-fees-over-covid-tweets-5321591%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Kulvinder%20Kaul%20Gill%2C%20a%20physician%20in%20Canada%20specialising%20in%20immunology%20and%20paediatrics%2C%20is%20now%20embroiled%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20stemming%20from%20her%20Covid-related%20tweets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Felon-musk-to-pay-indian-origin-doctor-kulvinder-kaur-gill-rs-2-crore-legal-fees-over-covid-tweets-5321591%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Completes%20Rare%20And%20Historic%20'Double%20Century'%20For%20Mumbai%20Indians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20star%20batter%20and%20former%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20playing%20his%20200th%20match%20in%20the%20league%20for%20his%20franchise%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20has%20been%20named%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20match%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20at%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20International%20Stadium%2C%20Hyderabad.%20SRH%20and%20MI%20are%20taking%20on%20each%20other%20in%20an%20IPL%202024%20clash%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Both%20teams%20started%20with%20narrow%20losses%20of%20four%20runs%20and%20six%20runs%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20and%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20their%20campaign%20openers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20legend%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20Since%20joining%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20bright%20up-and-coming%20talent%20back%20in%202011%2C%20Rohit%20has%20played%20199%20IPL%20matches%20in%20Blue%20and%20Gold%20clothing%2C%20scoring%205%2C084%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.39%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20129.86.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2034%20fifties%20in%20195%20innings%20for%20MI%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20109*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20over%20the%20captaincy%20of%20the%20franchise%20from%20Ricky%20Ponting%20in%202013%2C%20Rohit%20took%20MI%20to%20their%20golden%20period%2C%20winning%20the%20trophy%20five%20times%20in%2010%20years%20(2013%2C%202015%2C%202017%2C%202019%20and%202020)%20and%20reaching%20playoffs%20twice.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20replaced%20him%20as%20the%20captain%20last%20year%20after%20making%20a%20move%20to%20the%20franchise%20that%20made%20him%20a%20star%20following%20two%20great%20years%20with%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%2C%20including%20the%20title-winning%20debut%20season%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20has%20also%20won%20two%20Champions%20League%20T20%20titles%20with%20MI%20in%202011%20and%202013%2C%20the%20latter%20as%20a%20captain.%20The%20'Hitman'%20is%20MI's%20all-time%20highest%20run-getter%2C%20scoring%205%2C357%20runs%20in%20208%20matches%20and%20204%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.59%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20almost%20130%2C%20with%20a%20century%20and%2035%20fifties%20in%20204%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20youngster%2C%20Rohit%20also%20represented%20the%20now-defunct%20Deccan%20Chargers%2C%20a%20former%20Hyderabad%20franchise%20from%202008-2010.%20He%20played%2045%20matches%20for%20the%20team%2C%20scoring%201%2C170%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2030.79%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20131%2C%20with%20eight%20fifties%20in%2044%20innings.%20His%20best%20score%20was%2076*.%20He%20won%20the%20IPL%202009%20season%20with%20this%20franchise%2C%20making%20him%20a%20six-time%20IPL%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20batter%20is%20the%20fourth-highest%20run-getter%20in%20IPL%20history%2C%20scoring%206%2C254%20runs%20in%20244%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.63%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20130.15.%20He%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2042%20fifties%20in%20239%20innings%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20109*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20led%20MI%20for%20so%20long%2C%20Rohit%20is%20an%20institution%20in%20himself%2C%20with%20him%20and%20MI%20shaping%20the%20career%20trajectories%20of%20many%20future%20Indian%20stars%20like%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20Ambati%20Rayadu%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunrisers%20Hyderabad%20Squad%3A%20Mayank%20Agarwal%2C%20Abhishek%20Sharma%2C%20Rahul%20Tripathi%2C%20Aiden%20Markram%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen(w)%2C%20Abdul%20Samad%2C%20Shahbaz%20Ahmed%2C%20Marco%20Jansen%2C%20Pat%20Cummins(c)%2C%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20Mayank%20Markande%2C%20T%20Natarajan%2C%20Travis%20Head%2C%20Glenn%20Phillips%2C