al%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20said%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20served%20late%2C%20and%20that%20he%20needed%20time%20to%20study%20the%20document.%20Senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20said%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20filed%20on%20March%2023.%20%26quot%3BDefects%20were%20cured%20later.%20I%20am%20sure%20Mr%20Raju%20does%20not%20want%20us%20to%20serve%20a%20defective%20copy%20to%20him...%20we%20shared%20petition%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%20his%20arrest%20had%20violated%20his%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20alleged%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArrest%20without%20interrogation%20shows%20the%20current%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20argued%2C%20underlining%20the%20AAP's%20claim%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20was%20timed%20to%20disrupt%20the%20party's%20campaign%20for%20next%20month's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Mr%20Raju%20said%20the%20ED%20sought%20to%20file%20replies%20on%20the%20main%20matter%20and%20on%20the%20petition%20for%20interim%20relief.%20When%20the%20court%20pointed%20out%20it%20had%20already%20said%20it%20will%20issue%20a%20notice%20in%20the%20former%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20interim%20relief%20also%2C%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%20If%20I%20am%20not%20entitled%20to%20file%20a%20reply%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20hear%20me.%20I%20can't%20be%20deprived%20of%20my%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20last%20week%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20has%20roiled%20his%20AAP%20and%20provoked%20furious%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20this%20week%20sent%20to%20jail%20till%20March%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20believes%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%20provided%20an%20impossibly%20high%20profit%20margin%20of%20185%20per%20cent%20for%20retailers%20and%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20wholesalers.%20Of%20the%20latter%2C%20six%20per%20cent%20-%20over%20Rs%20600%20crore%20-%20were%20bribes%20and%20the%20money%20was%20allegedly%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20AAP's%20poll%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20labelled%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20this%20case%2C%20but%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20party%20colleagues%20arrested%20in%20this%20matter%20-%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20former%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20-%20have%20all%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20the%20opposition%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20for%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20like%20the%20ED%2C%20to%20target%20rivals%20and%20critics%20before%20the%20general%20election.%20The%20AAP%20has%20criticised%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20on%20grounds%20it%20was%20timed%20to%20interfere%20with%20his%20plans%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20dismissed%20claims%20it%20uses%20central%20agencies%20as%20described%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711546980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1o4sf5l8_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-relief-for-arvind-kejriwal-from-high-court-next-hearing-on-april-3-5321338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20spend%20at%20least%20another%20night%20in%20jail%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20a%20petition%20Wednesday%2C%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%