20homage%20to%20Kerala%2C%20our%20home%20state%2C%20where%20majestic%20elephants%20are%20treasured%20as%20part%20of%20our%20rich%20heritage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20care%20of%20your%20parents'%20brain%20health%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20starting%20point%20was%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20help%20parents%20feel%20less%20isolated%20and%20lonely%20as%20they%20stayed%20away%20from%20their%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20September%202023%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEstimates%20based%20on%20a%20recent%20multi-centric%20study%20reveal%20a%20dementia%20prevalence%20rate%20of%207.4%25%20among%20those%20aged%2060%20years%20and%20above%2C%20translating%20to%20nearly%209%20lakh%20Indians%20currently%20living%20with%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20an%20estimated%2088%20lakh%20in%202016%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20dementia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20to%201.7%20crore%20by%202036.%20The%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Prevalence%20of%20dementia%20in%20India%3A%20National%20and%20State%20estimates%20from%20a%20nationwide%20study%E2%80%99%20was%20published%20in%20July%20this%20year%20%5B2023%5D%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAlzheimer%E2%80%99s%20and%20Dementia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20journal%20of%20the%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20Association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%20at%20Ivory%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20research%20estimates%20show%20that%20one%20person%20in%20India%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20every%2020%20seconds.%20Contributing%20factors%20such%20as%20loneliness%2C%20increased%20nuclear%20families%20and%20sedentary%20lifestyles%20have%20added%20to%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20research%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20reports%20show%20that%20cases%20have%20increased%20from%20an%20estimated%205.3%20million%20in%202020%20to%208.8%20million%20in%202023.%20Furthermore%2C%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2070%2C%20even%20with%20mild%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20face%20a%201%20in%203%20chance%20of%20progressing%20to%20dementia%20within%20five%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20heightened%20dialogue%20and%20action%20in%20neuro%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Issac%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20Ivory%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20insufficient%20attention%20and%20understanding%20of%20dementia%2C%20especially%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20symptom%20identification%20tools%20combined%20with%20scant%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20advice%20at%20the%20right%20time%20makes%20this%20a%20pressing%20problem%20for%20every%20Indian%20household%20with%20an%20ageing%20parent.%20Urban%20seniors%2C%20particularly%20those%20living%20alone%2C%20face%20challenges%20in%20monitoring%20their%20cognitive%20health%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20%5BCOVID-19%5D%20pandemic-induced%20isolation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20Ivory%2C%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Ivory%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20developing%20a%20pioneering%20platform%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cognitive%20wellness%20of%20seniors%20and%20cultivating%20healthy%20brain%20habits.%20We%20offer%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20interactive%20content%2C%20social%20games%2C%20neuroscience-backed%20assessments%2C%20and%20comprehensive%20wellness%20programmes%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20cognitive%20well-being%20and%20mitigating%20the%20risk%20of%20brain-related%20ailments%20such%20as%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20this%20point%2C%20however%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy.%20As%20Issac%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20met%2C%20there%20were%20few%20ready%20reckoners%20and%20research%20available%20for%20companies%20who%20are%20building%20in%20age-tech%2C%20particularly%20in%20India%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20take%20any%20existing%20learnings%20and%20apply%20them%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20seniors.%20That%20meant%20that%20we%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20multiple%20product%20concepts%20parallelly%20before%20zeroing%20down%20on%20what%20would%20find%20mass%20pain-point%20resonance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurship%20in%20the%20field%20of%20brain%20health%20is%20still%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20built%20these%20learnings%2C%20we%20also%20realised%20that%20the%20VC%20ecosystem%20was%20still%20warming%20up%20to%20this%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20many%20funds%20have%20stepped%20forward%20to%20support%20AgeTech%20companies%2C%2018%20months%20ago%2C%20we%20had%20to%20build%20conviction%20about%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20AgeTech%20space%20in%20the%20venture%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20Ivory%20successfully%20raised%20%24500%2C000%20(Rs%204.13%20crore)%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Capital%20A%2C%20an%20early-stage%20VC%20fund%2C%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20fundraiser%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20bridge%20these%20gaps%20by%20offering%20a%20tech-driven%20platform%20that%20makes%20clinical%20tools%20and%20expertise%20for%20better%20brain%20health%20accessible%20to%20millions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Issac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201741px)%20100vw%2C%201741px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221741%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navigating%20brain%20health%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397.jpg%201741w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-500x353.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-768x543.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-1536x1085.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345587%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIvory%20%E2%80%98Fact%20Sheet%E2%80%99%20on%20Dementia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20seniors%20navigate%20brain%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sumiti%20Saharan%2C%20a%20neuroscientist%20with%20over%2015%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20neurodegenerative%20disorders%20and%20dementia%20research%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%202050%2C%20one%20in%20five%20individuals%20will%20be%20elderly%20in%20India.%20The%20urgency%20for%20innovative%20solutions%20for%20dementia%20detection%20and%20management%20has%20become%20undeniable.%20Evidence-based%20solutions%20like%20Ivory%20offer%20a%20scalable%20and%20accessible%20mechanism%20for%20redefining%20the%20dementia%20care%20journey%20and%20empowering%20the%20elderly%20to%20live%20a%20healthy%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20Ivory%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341821%2Fsenior-citizen-couples-madhav-damle-matchmaking-agency-live-in-relationships-valentines-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%20%3C%2Fa%3Enavigate%20their%20brain%20health%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rahul%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20concerned%20users%20and%20their%20families%20who%20want%20to%20understand%20if%20their%20memory%20lapses%20are%20stress%20related%20or%20something%20which%20warrants%20more%20attention%2C%20Ivory%20provides%20the%20equivalent%20of%20your%20annual%20health%20checkup%20for%20your%20brain.%20This%20checkup%20is%20done%20through%20cognitive%20assessments%20and%20neuro-psychological%20evaluations%2C%20which%20help%20you%20profile%20your%20brain%20health%20status%20and%20potential%20cognitive%20impairment%20or%20dementia%20risk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTowards%20this%20end%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20partnered%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cognifit.com%2Fassessment-scientific-validation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECognifit%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20a%20scientifically%20validated%20and%20leading%20brain%20training%20and%20cognitive%20assessments%20company%20%E2%80%94%20to%20provide%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20tests.%20Their%20battery%20of%20tests%20have%20been%20developed%20with%20more%20than%2020%20years%20of%20inputs%20and%20research%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Issac%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20cognitive%20test%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20inputs%20which%20go%20into%20assessing%20someone%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20as%20every%20user%20is%20unique%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20cultural%20and%20sociological%20background.%20These%20assessments%20provide%20a%20cognitive%20report%20across%20various%20skills%2C%20and%20post%20that%2C%20more%20focussed%20assessments%20are%20carried%20out.%20Hence%2C%20every%20report%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20user%20is%20combined%20with%20a%20human%20interaction%20with%20a%20neuro%20counsellor%20to%20give%20a%20holistic%20risk%20assessment.%20Neuropsychologists%20then%20use%20these%20reports%20in%20consonance%20with%20their%20subjective%20examination%20of%20the%20patient%20to%20propose%20alternative%20lifestyle-based%20interventions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20neuropsychologist%20does%20employ%20a%20third-party%20assessment%20mechanism%20like%20a%20Mini-Mental%20State%20Examination%20(MMSE)%2C%20or%20a%20Montreal%20Cognitive%20Assessment%20(MoCA)%2C%20or%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)-NCTB%20(Neuro%20Cognitive%20Tool%20Box)%2C%20or%20Addenbrooke%E2%80%99s%20Cognitive%20Examination%20(ACE)-III%20test.%20It%20is%20the%20combination%20of%20the%20test%20used%20along%20with%20a%20subjective%20interpretation%20and%20continuous%20tracking%20that%20makes%20for%20a%20more%20definitive%20assessment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20cognitive%20and%20neuro-psychological%20assessments%2C%20counsellors%20hired%20by%20the%20startup%20suggest%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%20which%20could%20include%20further%20clinical%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20proactive%20users%2C%20who%20would%20just%20want%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20keeping%20themselves%20mentally%20active%20and%20take%20a%20preventive%20approach%20towards%20brain%20health%2C%20we%20have%20our%20app%20which%20offers%20daily%20quizzes%2C%20brain%20games%2C%20and%20daily%20tips%20for%20an%20active%20lifestyle%20leading%20to%20reduced%20impairment%20risk.%20We%20have%20also%20developed%20a%20personalised%20brain%20workout%20daily%2C%20calibrated%20to%20improve%20the%20skills%20they%20lag%20in.%20The%20daily%20workout%20currently%20consists%20of%202%20games%20and%20a%20mini-assessment%20to%20measure%20progress.%20Going%20ahead%20we%20will%20be%20developing%20our%20proprietary%20workouts%20as%20we%20understand%20more%20about%20these%20users.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20how%20the%20user%20performs%2C%20either%20the%20difficulty%20level%20or%20the%20games%20are%20then%20changed%20on%20an%20ongoing%20basis.%20The%20user%20will%20also%20get%20charts%20of%20progress%20that%20they%20can%20see%20across%20the%20skills%20he%20is%20being%20tested%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20A%20good%20starting%20point%20for%20this%20is%20the%20current%20cognitive%20age%20test%20that%20they%20have%20live%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.liveivory.com%2Fcognitive-age%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%20on%20mobile%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20daily%20tips%20they%20offer%20are%20live%20on%20their%20social%20media%20pages%2C%20which%20can%20be%20accessed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fletsliveivory%3Figsh%3DOGQ5ZDc2ODk2ZA%253D%253D%26utm_source%3Dqr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20close%20to%2050%20different%20games%20with%20different%20levels%20of%20difficulty%20that%20will%20also%20be%20live%20on%20our%20app.%20These%20test%20different%20skills%2C%20such%20as%20auditory%20skills%2C%20hand-eye%20coordination%2C%20visual%20reasoning%2C%20focus%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20short-term%20memory%2C%20among%2023%20different%20skills.%20The%20app%20is%20currently%20in%20its%20beta%20version%20slated%20for%20further%20testing%20but%20contains%20various%20games%20%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20we%20have%20a%20game%20which%20tests%20processing%20speed%2C%20estimation%2C%20and%20spatial%20perception.%20Apart%20from%20these%20cognitive%20games%2C%20Ivory%20also%20has%20a%20gamified%20quizzing%20experience%20in%20version%201%20across%20topics%20of%20interest%20for%20our%20target%20group%20(TG)%20apart%20from%20ongoing%20brain-teasers%20that%20we%20will%20soon%20drop%20on%20the%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jwala%20Narayanan%2C%20a%20consulting%20neuropsychologist%20at%20Annaswamy%20Mudaliar%20Hospital%20and%20Manipal%20Hospital%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20understand%20that%20dementia%20risks%20are%20diverse%2C%20making%20prevention%20a%20crucial%20strategy%20in%20the%20battle%20against%20it.%20Given%20the%20considerable%20challenges%20of%20behaviour%20change%2C%20Ivory%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20healthcare%20ecosystem%20becomes%20essential%2C%20harnessing%20technology%E2%80%99s%20advantages%20to%20inspire%20a%20positive%20shift%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20habits%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%