%20fires%20to%20protect%20their%20land.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPritam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20young%20volunteers%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20charge%20against%20forest%20fires%20to%20protect%20their%20land.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommitment%20to%20protect%20the%20village%20from%20forest%20fires%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20young%20people%20who%20migrate%20to%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20better%20job%20opportunities%2C%20Pritam%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20his%20village%20after%20completing%20his%20higher%20studies%20in%202022.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20leave%20my%20native%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20graduate%20with%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%20(BA)%20degree%2C%20Pritam%20is%20currently%20preparing%20for%20the%20Government%20examinations%20and%20has%20volunteered%20to%20become%20a%20firefighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Pauri%20Garhwal%2C%20Pritam%20says%20that%20he%20has%20witnessed%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F217451%2Farunachal-ifs-officer-hero-prevent-forest-fire-award-winning-innovation-governance-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20fires%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20dreadful%202022%20fires.%20%