ny%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Pritam%2C%20THF%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20of%20preventing%20forest%20fire%20has%20seen%205%2C066%20young%20firefighters%20being%20trained%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20under%2010%20development%20blocks%20of%20Pauri%20Garhwal%2C%20Tehri%20Garhwal%2C%20Almora%2C%20and%20Bageshwar%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20THF%20has%20also%20enhanced%20community%20resilience%20by%20reviving%20the%20%E2%80%98Van%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20local%20community%20group%20responsible%20for%20forest%20management%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encouraging%20the%20plantation%20of%20fire-resistant%20species%2C%20and%20raising%20awareness%20through%20%3Cem%3ENukkad%20Natak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(street%20play)%2C%20rallies%2C%20wall%20writing%2C%20quiz%20competition%2C%20radio%20programs%2C%20and%20jingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20region%20has%20observed%20a%20significant%20decrease%20of%20about%2053.33%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20from%2030%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%202019-21%20to%2