orce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen-led%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20risen%20to%2018%20percent%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20But%20while%20this%20is%20a%20poster%20story%20of%20the%20success%20that%20the%20female%20entrepreneurial%20world%20has%20witnessed%2C%20another%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EDealStreetAsia%3C%2Fem%3E%20claims%20that%20startups%20founded%20by%20women%20received%20only%200.3%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20venture%20capital%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20growth%20is%20a%20series%20of%20small%20steps%2C%20Cisco%20and%20Villgro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator%20%E2%80%94%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20joint%20initiative%2C%20%E2%80%98Tvaran%E2%80%99%2C%20whose%20intent%20is%20to%20introduce%20progressive%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20women-led%20startups%20are%20being%20empowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20cohort%2C%20launched%20in%20October%202022%2C%20met%20its%20goal%20of%20accelerating%20women%20entrepreneurs%20driving%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20sector%20by%20providing%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20specifically%20climate%20action%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalyani%20Krishna%2C%20Manager%2C%20Gender%20Inclusion%20Villgro%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman-induced%20climate%20change%20is%20not%20just%20hearsay%2C%20she%20cautions.%20A%202020%20research%20initiative%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Climate%20Change%20Research%20(CCCR)%20in%20India%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20(MoES)%20revealed%20a%20rise%20of%200.7%20degrees%20Celsius%20surface%20air%20temperature%20from%201901%20to%202018%20and%20a%20rise%20of%201%20degree%20Celsius%20sea%20surf